OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781093477
OL,3,CData shows pupils skipped school for
OL,4,CTaylor Swift concert
OL,6,FData shows there was a spike in school
OL,7,Fabsence around the time of the Taylor
OL,8,FSwift concerts in Liverpool in 2024.
OL,10,FThe American singer performed two gigs
OL,11,Fat Anfield during her Eras tour on
OL,12,FThursday June 13 and Friday June 14
OL,13,F2024.
OL,15,FThe Department for Education found
OL,16,Fspikes in the absence rate of
OL,17,Fschoolgirls in the Liverpool local
OL,18,Fauthority on those dates, particularly
OL,19,Ffor Year 9 and Year 10 girls on the
OL,20,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
