PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781093477
OL,3,CData shows pupils skipped school for
OL,4,CTaylor Swift concert
OL,6,FThe rate rose from 12.9% on the Friday
OL,7,Fbefore to 14.9% on the Friday of the
OL,8,Fconcert for girls in Year 9, while the
OL,9,Frate increased from 12.6% to 16.4% for
OL,10,Fgirls in the year above on the same
OL,11,Fdates.
OL,13,FIt also found absence rates were
OL,14,Fhigher across all year groups on days
OL,15,Fthat coincided with pupil's birthdays.
OL,17,FThis was the most prominent among Year
OL,18,F8 pupils.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
