PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781093477
OL,3,CData shows pupils skipped school for
OL,4,CTaylor Swift concert
OL,6,FAcross Year 8 in the 2024/25 academic
OL,7,Fyear, the average absence rate stood
OL,8,Fat 12.8% for days that coincided with
OL,9,Fa pupil's birthday, and at 8.3% for
OL,10,Fall other days.
OL,12,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We've seen five million more
OL,14,Fdays in the classroom last year ` the
OL,15,Fbiggest improvement in attendance in a
OL,16,Fdecade.
OL,18,F"That's real progress, but there is
OL,19,Fmore to do.
OL,26,@uD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
