OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781093477
OL,3,CData shows pupils skipped school for
OL,4,CTaylor Swift concert
OL,6,F"Improving attendance is everyone's
OL,7,Fresponsibility.
OL,9,F"That's why we're giving schools
OL,10,Fbetter tools to identify problems
OL,11,Fearly and work with families to
OL,12,Faddress them, while encouraging
OL,13,Fparents to play their part in building
OL,14,Fstrong attendance habits.
OL,16,F"By sharing what works and backing our
OL,17,Fwider reforms to make schools places
OL,18,Fwhere children feel they belong, want
OL,19,Fto be and can achieve and thrive,
OL,20,Ftogether we can ensure more children
OL,21,Fare in the classroom every day."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUxD@AOU}D@`O]
